data.name: label2.Text
data.value: This is the basis at which you will figure out what caloric amount you “maintain,” meaning you should not gain or lose weight at this food amount. You will notice a lot of online calculators will use a lot of complicated formulas to spit out a number for you to give you a baseline. While this method is no different, it is much quicker and easy for you to remember.
